Com aviDemoTics (cvar)
======================

Description
-----------

This determines the framerate to capture .[TGA](TGA\_(file\_format)) frames generated with the [aviDemo](AviDemo\_(console\_command)) command.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

`com_aviDemoTicsÂ [int]`

Parameters
----------

-   [int] - The framerate to capture at.
    -   1 = 15fps
    -   2 = 30fps
    -   3 = 45fps
    -   4 = 60fps

