Notes
-----

Any number above four seems to have no effect. It's not 100% clear if this it based on the engine's in-game clock of 60fps or if it's based on the refresh rate. Related CVars:

-   [com\_aviDemoHeight](Com\_aviDemoHeight\_(cvar)) - You can select the height of each frame.
-   [com\_aviDemoSamples](Com\_aviDemoSamples\_(cvar)) - You can select the [antialiasing](Antialiasing) factor of each frame.
-   [com\_aviDemoWidth](Com\_aviDemoWidth\_(cvar)) - You can select the width of each frame.


